OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,FThe driver of a coach carrying
OL,7,Fschoolchildren which crashed on the
OL,8,FA36 in Hampshire says he takes full
OL,9,Fresponsibility for what happened.
OL,11,FThe vehicle left the southbound
OL,12,Fcarriageway between the Ower
OL,13,FRoundabout and junction 2 of the M27
OL,14,Fjust after 5am on 25 December 2025,
OL,15,Fand ended up in a ditch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
