PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,FToday (Monday 23 February) the driver,
OL,7,FBrett Jarvis, 48, of Honey Hill in
OL,8,FLambourn, appeared at Aldershot
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court, where he pleaded
OL,10,Fguilty to one charge of driving
OL,11,Fwithout due care and attention.
OL,13,FHe was fined a total of #546 and given
OL,14,F6 penalty points.
OL,16,FAs he already had 6 points on his
OL,17,Flicence the judge disqualified him for
OL,18,Fsix months from driving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,7,FMeridian Brett Jarvis admitted he
OL,8,Fcan't recall what happened, but
OL,9,Fdescribed the incident as 'a freak
OL,10,Faccident'.
OL,12,F"I came off the bottom roundabout no
OL,13,Fproblem, just travelling up towards
OL,14,Fthe M27.
OL,16,F"There was a jolt and I tried to save
OL,17,Fit, but I couldn't.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,F"My main concern was the kids - I
OL,7,Fdidn't care about myself. I was very
OL,8,Fupset, trying to make sure the kids
OL,9,Fwere fine.
OL,11,F"The ambulance crews tried to sort me
OL,12,Fout, but I refused until I knew
OL,13,Feveryone was fine."
OL,15,FThe coach being driven by Mr Jarvis
OL,16,Fwas taking pupils and staff on their
OL,17,Fway to Normandy for a school history
OL,18,Ftrip.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,FThe school confirmed 29 school
OL,7,Fchildren and five adults were on
OL,8,Fboard, including the driver, and two
OL,9,Fadults sustained minor injuries.
OL,11,FAsked if he bears the responsibility
OL,12,Fof the crash Brett Jarvis added: "100%
OL,13,FI do - there's no-one else to blame.
OL,15,F"I was driving, and I bear what
OL,16,Fconsequences are dealt to me today.
OL,18,F"if I could turn back time and try and
OL,19,Ftake it back, but what's happened has
OL,20,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,F"I can't turn back time."
OL,8,FA spokesperson for Badminton School
OL,9,Fsaid: "We have been informed by
OL,10,FHampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,11,FConstabulary that today, (23 February
OL,12,F2026) at Aldershot Magistrates' Court,
OL,13,Fthe driver of a coach pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto driving without due care and
OL,15,Fattention following a single vehicle
OL,16,Fcollision on the A36 roundabout and
OL,17,Fjunction 2 of the M27, on 25 September
OL,18,F2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879289
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,F"The accident involved a coach
OL,7,Fcarrying Badminton School, Bristol,
OL,8,Fpupils and staff on their way to
OL,9,FNormandy for a school history trip on
OL,10,F25 September 2025.
OL,12,F"The vehicle had 29 school children
OL,13,Fand five adults on board, including
OL,14,Fthe driver, and two adults sustained
OL,15,Fminor injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
