OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1771879290
OL,3,CCoach driver banned from driving
OL,4,Cfollowing school bus crash in Hampshire
OL,6,F"Badminton School would like to thank
OL,7,Fthe emergency services in attendance
OL,8,Fon the day and commend the behaviour
OL,9,Fof all the pupils involved and the
OL,10,Fcare and professionalism of the school
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,F"The school will make no further
OL,14,Fcomment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
